title: Looking for A Bigger Place…Try Us
posting_body: ['The Emerson Apartments is located in Tacoma’s Stadium District, which is named after the historic Stadium High School.', 'The Emerson Apartments is just blocks away from the wonderful Pantages Theater and the Tacoma Comedy Club.', 'Utilities are additional, charged separately.', 'For more information or to schedule a tour, please call our office:', 'show contact info', 'or feel free to email me at:', 'show contact info', '.', 'You can apply online at: <URL>', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday: 9am-5pm', 'Saturday-Sunday: CLOSED', 'Apartment Home Features:', '*Spacious Floor Plans', '*Refrigerator', '*Stove', '*Spacious Closet', 'Amenities:', '*Easy access to I-5.', '*Pet Friendly.', '*Secured Entry.', '*On-site Laundry.', 'QUALIFICATIONS:', '**Must have 2.85 times rent in gross monthly income', '**Must have NO evictions in past 7 years', '**Must NOT owe any money to any apartments/rental companies', '**Must NOT have an open bankruptcy', '**Collections/past due balances must not be over $3,000(excluding medical/student loans)', 'Visit our website for this and many other great properties at: <URL>/', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
